<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7895136>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–10. Habitus and head of adult Sorolopha. 1. Habitus of S. plinthograpta (Meyrick, 1931), male, Wakayama. 2. Head of S. plinthograpta. 3. Habitus of S. sugiurai sp. nov. (holotype), male, Wakayama. 4. Head of S. sugiurai. 5. Habitus of S. viridis sp. nov. (holotype), male, Gifu. 6. Head of S. viridis. 7. Habitus of S. sphaerocopa (Meyrick, 1930), female, Amami Ôshima Is. 8. Head of S. sphaerocopa. 9. Habitus of S. baribaris sp. nov. (holotype), male, Wakayama. 10. Head of S. baribaris." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7895136/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7895138>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–15. Male genitalia of Sorolopha. 11. S. plinthograpta (Meyrick, 1931), Wakayama. 12. S. sugiurai sp. nov. (holotype), Wakayama. 13. S. viridis sp. nov. (holotype), Gifu. 14. S. sphaerocopa (Meyrick, 1930), Yakushima Is. 15. S. baribaris sp. nov. (holotype), Wakayama." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7895138/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7895140>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–20. Female genitalia of Sorolopha. 16. S. plinthograpta (Meyrick, 1931), Wakayama. 17. S. sugiurai sp. nov. (paratype), Wakayama. 18. S. viridis sp. nov. (paratype), Wakayama. 19. S. sphaerocopa (Meyrick, 1930), Amami Ôshima Is. 20. S. baribaris sp. nov. (paratype), Wakayama." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7895140/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7895142>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21–22. Leaf shelters formed by Sorolopha larvae. 21. A leaf shelter formed by olethreutine larvae on Actinodaphne acuminata. Adults of S. plinthograpta, S. sugiurai sp. nov., and S. baribaris sp. nov., emerge from the leaf shelter. 22. A leaf shelter formed by S. viridis larvae on Illicium anisatum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7895142/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

